====Usage notes====
The word is now written as {{zh-l|僚|tr=-}}, as this form, {{l-self|zh|獠}}, is deemed a {{w|Graphic pejoratives in written Chinese|graphic pejorative}} with its "beast" radical. Some of the peoples referred to as {{l-self|zh|獠}} in ancient texts have been identified as [[Kra-Dai]] speaking peoples by modern scholarship.

